Late Springboks wing, Chester Williams was laid to rest on Saturday. His funeral was held today at Newlands rugby stadium in Cape Town. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Chloe Williams, the daughter of Springboks legend has paid a heartfelt tribute to her father. The late Springboks wing was laid to rest on Saturday. His funeral was held on Saturday at Newlands Rugby Stadium in Cape Town. Former teammates, dignitaries, family and friends all remembered one of South Africa's most popular players. WATCH: Chester Williams laid to rest Rugby legend Mornè du Plessis and Williams' daughter spoke of the impact he had on so many people. Williams died last Friday from a heart attack. He was 49.